progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg" width="779" height="824" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:824,&quot;width&quot;:779,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:137882,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38deeaa6-e325-4d56-8807-96a7fc105489_779x824.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.commonwealthfund.org/blog/2022/us-maternal-mortality-crisis-continues-worsen-international-comparison">联邦基金</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-maternal-mortality-hits-highest-level-since-1965-f9829776">近年来，这一数字只会变得更糟</a>。</p><p>这加剧了美国作为一个正在衰落国家的整体感觉。这似乎与我们较低且不断下降的预期寿命、价格过高的医疗保健等等有关。许多人都知道这一事实导致了 2010 年代末的普遍危机感。</p><p>只是有一个小问题：<em>最近的增长可能根本就没有发生</em>。从 2003 年开始，美国各州开始对死亡证明进行修改——在死亡时勾选怀孕的复选框。这导致更多的死亡被贴上与怀孕相关的标签。<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC8055191/">约瑟夫等人。 （2021）</a>讲故事：</p><blockquote><p>美国国家卫生统计中心进行的严格研究表明，此前报道的美国孕产妇死亡率上升是监测变化的结果。 2003年修订后的死亡证明中引入了怀孕复选框，并由各州以交错的方式实施，导致孕产妇死亡的确认和报告的孕产妇死亡率的增加。本文[论文]总结了国家卫生统计中心报告的调查结果……[C]2002 年至 2018 年间，孕产妇死亡率没有显着变化，[并且]年龄调整分析显示，孕产妇死亡率暂时下降了 [21%]。死亡率……不受怀孕复选框影响的孕产妇死亡的具体原因，例如先兆子痫，显示出显着的时间下降。</p></blockquote><p>这是一个图表： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe4fa8b9c-e6d8-47d3-914e-1eb87be58d30_796x448.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe4fa8b9c-e6d8-47d3-914e-1eb87be58d30_796x448.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2F