" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这并不像英联邦图表那么糟糕，但也不是很好（韩国到底怎么了？？）。美国在降低孕产妇死亡率方面仍有大量工作要做。但就像 2010 年代的许多衰落论叙述一样，这个故事并没有我们想象的那么戏剧化。</p><h4>美国最愚蠢的经济统计数据再次来袭</h4><p>说到夸大的危机叙事，大多数美国人“靠工资过活”的想法怎么样？你看到很多人都提出这样的说法，包括令人尊敬的伯尼·桑德斯： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg" width="676" height="274.2333696837514" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:372,&quot;width&quot;:917,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:676,&quot;bytes&quot;:80056,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F016ed3d6-e60d-413c-a4b4-26e87f1eec67_917x372.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>现在，我支持劳工部的规则改变。但大多数美国人“靠工资过活”的陈词滥调确实需要退休。从经济统计数据来看，这是最假的。</p><p>基本上，发生的事情是像 LendingClub 这样的私营公司<a href="https://www.bankrate.com/finance/credit-cards/living-paycheck-to-paycheck-statistics/">四处询问人们</a>“你是靠工资生活吗？”大多数人都说是的。然后这些数字就会<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/10/31/62percent-of-americans-still-live-paycheck-to-paycheck-amid-inflation.html">被财经媒体报道，</a>就好像它们是某种经济事实一样。但他们不是。因为“靠工资生活”没有明确的含义。</p><p> “靠工资生活”是否意味着：</p><ul><li><p>你的存款为零？</p></li><li><p>您的积蓄太少而无法舒适吗？</p></li><li><p>您的<em>流动性</em>储蓄为零或不足——银行里的现金，而不是您退休账户中的股票？</p></li><li><p>您通常一个月内没有积累任何财富吗？</p></li><li><p>您在退休帐户中存钱并每月还清抵押贷款，但您不增加流动现金？</p></li><li><p>如果没有下一份薪水，您就无法支付每月的账单吗？</p></li><li><p>您只是期待每个月收到薪水吗？</p></li></ul><p>没人知道。对于许多回答“是”的不同人来说，这可能意味着许多不同的事情。因此，请停止引用“薪水到薪水”的数字。这是没有意义的。</p><p>事实证明，一些经济学家确实研究了关于美国人拥有多少财务缓冲的明确数据。 2022 年消费者财务调查发现，约 98.6% 的美国家庭拥有支票账户或类似账户，这些账户中的金额中位数<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/great-news-about-american-wealth">为 8000 美元</a>。 2016 年，约 76% 的美国人<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/econres/notes/feds-notes/assessing-families-liquid-savings-using-the-survey-of-consumer-finances-20181119.html">银行存款超过 400 美元</a>——较 2000 年代中期有所增加。 2013 年至 2019 年间，表示愿意选择通过支付现金支付 400 美元意外费用的美国人比例从 50% 上升至 63%： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg" width="555" height="369" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:369,&quot;width&quot;:555,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:45382,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53075fad-8e5b-4d07-8061-93590df71195_555x369.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/2020-economic-well-being-of-us-households-in-2019-dealing-with-unexpected-expenses.htm">FRB</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>只有<a href="https://www.federalreserve.gov/publications/2020-economic-well-being-of-us-households-in-2019-dealing-with-unexpected-expenses.htm">12% 的人表示他们无法支付</a>400 美元的费用。</p><p>现在，12% 的美国人无法支付 400 美元的费用，这远远高于应有的水平！但这与你所看到的声称“靠工资生活”的人数相差甚远。金融不安全是我们绝对应该认真对待的另一个经济问题，但流行的危机和衰退叙述被夸大了。</p><h4>新闻越来越负面</h4><p>为什么如此多的负面叙述成为美国新闻观众的普遍看法？我认为，部分原因是 2010 年代末的普遍动荡，部分原因是外部政治派系传递的信息，他们希望通过制造国家陷入危机的感觉来获利。但新闻媒体本身在过去几十年里变得越来越消极。</p><p>宾斯伯根等人。有<a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32026">一篇新论文</a>，其中他们使用文本挖掘来分析报纸中使用的语言。他们构建了对经济和非经济新闻的积极与消极情绪的衡量标准。在短期内，他们的经济情绪指标与经济事件相对应——经济衰退或通胀带来负面情绪，经济繁荣带来积极情绪。但从长期来看，经济和非经济景气多年来一直处于下降趋势： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg" width="802" height="710" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:710,&quot;width&quot;:802,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:151437,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32dc79af-6940-47fc-8039-e3b89af4c7fb_802x710.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.nber.org/papers/w32026">Binsbergen 等人。 (2024)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这里发生了什么？众所周知，<a href="https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.1908369116">大量</a><a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41562-023-01538-4">研究</a>表明，<a href="https://www.vox.com/the-highlight/23596969/bad-news-negativity-bias-media">新闻存在负面偏见</a>——坏消息比好消息更受关注，这使得媒体有动力强调和过度报道坏消息。近年来，随着新闻媒体的竞争越来越激烈，这种趋势可能有所加剧。放松管制和新技术带来的竞争加剧可能迫使报纸为了生存而变得越来越危言耸听和消极。</p><p>我想到的另一个假设是，从地方新闻转向全国新闻可能会导致更多负面消息。我找不到关于当地新闻是否比全国新闻更积极的研究，但人们确实倾向于认为当地经济比全国经济更好： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg" width="850" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:850,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:92951,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42b59379-30f2-4532-bf7e-6a0aa74baadf_850x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_