t;:&quot;8f41b8d1-dafb-4f02-9b2f-a9ac890fa064&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&#8220;I may be right and I may be wrong/ But you&#8217;re gonna miss me when I&#8217;m gone&#8221; &#8212; Taj Mahal Yesterday, as you may have heard, Hamas launched a massive surprise attack on Israel, crossing the border from Gaza and seizing or assaulting towns nearby after a huge rocket bombardment,&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;You're not going to like what comes after Pax Americana&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-10-07T20:04:38.107Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe5cb9f9c-05bf-46c1-97a7-71c0631ddebf_1123x751.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/youre-not-going-to-like-what-comes&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:137756417,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:939,&quot;comment_count&quot;:334,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}"></div><p>有些人不可避免地会声称后来的事件证明我错了。以色列-加沙战争开始后，美国海军在地中海<a href="https://news.usni.org/2023/10/09/gerald-r-ford-carrier-strike-group-stationed-in-mediterranean-to-deter-hezbollah-iran">驻扎</a>了三个月，这可能阻止了真主党加入战斗。美国对<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-carries-out-two-air-strikes-against-iran-aligned-groups-syria-official-2023-11-12/">叙利亚</a>和<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-forces-attacked-iraq-airbase-respond-self-defence-us-officials-2023-11-21/">伊拉克</a>境内伊朗支持的民兵组织的打击可能也有助于防止冲突在整个地区蔓延。与此同时，竞争对手看起来并非所向无敌。正如许多人<a href="https://twitter.com/SwannMarcus89/status/1745603741682741365">指出的</a>那样，俄罗斯仍在与一个小得多、穷得多的邻国进行全面战争，而中国正在整顿军队，并与经济放缓作斗争。</p><p>今天对胡塞武装的袭击——<a href="https://twitter.com/osint_69/status/1745591763165687873">据报道</a>已经打死了该民兵组织的一名领导人——似乎进一步证明了“美国治下的和平”仍然牢固存在。这些袭击是对红海航运的一系列袭击的回应，这些袭击实际上关闭了世界主要海运贸易路线之一： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg" width="842" height="814" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:814,&quot;width&quot;:842,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:135945,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa3cd0551-c87d-4632-b100-2fef36d77581_842x814.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://www.cfr.org/in-brief/how-houthi-attacks-red-sea-threaten-global-shipping">CFR</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>打击海盗、保护国际海上贸易是美国自建国以来一直在做的事情。<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marines%27_Hymn">海军陆战队的赞美诗中</a>提到了“的黎波里海岸”；这是指第一次巴巴里战争，当时新成立的美国派出船只与奥斯曼帝国支持的北非海盗作战。所以这看起来似乎一切如常。</p><p>但事实是，美国实在无法承受这场冲突。由于全球部署、财政紧缩和工业疲软，中国的海军资源非常紧张，而此时中国海军的建设有可能在其最关键的战区超越并压倒美国。问题是，全世界基本上已经习惯了美国在过去75年里单枪匹马保护整个世界的海洋。因此，现在，他们没有在美国能力捉襟见肘时挺身而出，而是搭便车并期望美国做它一直以来所做的事情。</p><p>这是非常危险的，因为如果美国的海上力量达到极限——或者在<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/were-not-ready-for-the-big-one">与中国的战争</a>中被摧毁——世界将突然发现自己失去了整个全球经济所依赖的海上贸易的守护者。</p><h4>海运贸易对全球繁荣至关重要</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/world-commerce-is-dependent-on-americas">阅读更多</a></p>; 
Techno-optimism for 2024What you should be excited about https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-2024 https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-2024Noah Smith Wed, 10 Jan 2024 07:10:12 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg" width="704" height="704" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1024,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:704,&quot;bytes&quot;:179930,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F454aa8dc-ee51-49e4-960b-58d22f399a92_1024x1024.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption"> <a href="http://@terrorproforma">@terrorproforma</a>的艺术</figcaption></figure></div><p>对于那些最近开始阅读 Noahpinion 的人，我在 2020 年底创建了<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-the-2020s">一个明确的技术乐观主义博客</a>。Covid 疫苗的成功和可再生能源的爆炸给了我希望，即 2010 年代的传统智慧是错误的，而技术毕竟<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/thoughts-on-techno-optimism">真的可以解决我们很多问题</a>。</p><p>从那以后的岁月，这种感觉更加强烈。自从我第一次开始相信咆哮的 20 年代以来，我们至少获得了两个巨大的技术惊喜：生成人工智能方面绝对令人惊叹的进步，以及历史上第一个真正有效的<a href="https://www.science.org/content/article/breakthrough-of-the-year-2023">抗肥胖药物</a>的出现。这些突破似乎来自左翼领域，有点像 mRNA 疫苗，但这是一种幻觉；在所有这三种情况下，多年的努力工作和渐进的进步突然达到了该技术已准备好迎接黄金时期的地步。这意味着在未来的几年里，我们可能还会遇到更多这样的惊喜；十年还有六年！</p><p>为什么所有这些突破都出现在同一个十年内？我认为部分原因与<a href="https://www.frbsf.org/economic-research/publications/working-papers/2023/07/">2005 年生产率下降</a>有关。当计算机化和早期互联网带来的生产力爆发逐渐减弱时，一些私人资本和政府拨款专注于渐进式改进，但另一些则寻求长期突破，以重新点燃快速进步。现在我怀疑其中许多努力正在取得成果。我认为另一个因素是，过去十年的大部分时间里，经济一直表现强劲，这为企业提供了闲置现金和动力（高劳动力成本）来进行创新。</p><p> 2021 年和 2022 年，生产力似乎持平，这引发了人们对“咆哮的 20 年代”这一想法的很多怀疑。但到了 2023 年，似乎又<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-roaring-20s-are-back-on-track">重新加速</a>了： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F057f98f0-68d3-4a3e-b9f2-38a792e21a25_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F057f98f0-68d3-4a3e-b9f2-38a792e21a25_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F057f98f0-68d3-4a3e-b9f2-38a792e21a25_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F057f98f0-68d3-4a3e-b9f2-38a792e21a25_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F057f98f0-68d3-4a3e-b9f2-38a792e21a25_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%