iv></div></figure></div><p>对于<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1743594071929844164">奇幻插画</a>来说，他们几乎可以与所有在世的人类艺术家媲美。</p><p>我对人工智能艺术比法学硕士更乐观的原因是训练数据的可用性。<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2211.04325.pdf">维拉洛博斯等人。 （2022）</a>表明，高质量的语言数据将在 2020 年代初到中期耗尽（假设没有合成数据），但图像数据直到 2040 年代才会耗尽： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg" width="1345" height="557" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:557,&quot;width&quot;:1345,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:228241,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb3b88acd-fb70-4032-b2f2-18a80828e5d1_1345x557.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2211.04325.pdf">Villalobos 等人。 (2022)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>新的图像数据（至少在某些类型上）比高质量的人类生成的语言数据更容易生成——只需派出一堆无人机去拍摄数万亿张照片即可。</p><p>因此，尽管人工智能艺术正在变得越来越好，但我认为它有潜力以惊人的速度不断变得更好。焦点已经从静态图像转移到<a href="https://medium.com/@artturi-jalli/ai-video-generators-14312e5bcb62">视频生成</a>。显然，这将为我们的信息生态系统造成一些问题，因为DeepFake视频泛滥 - 有些人认为Deepfakes可能已经<a href="https://www.wired.co.uk/article/slovakia-election-deepfakes">在斯洛伐克进行了选举</a>。但是，将现实的视频产生触摸到每个人的指尖将绝对改变生活。 （我可能会用它来制作<a href="https://twitter.com/Noahpinion/status/1744661100774449292">巨型兔子</a>的电影。） </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0d4ab37d-410b-40b9-942a-738f61b0f1a0_900x900.jpeg" width="636" height="636" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.